claim: Joaquin Phoenix did not earn a Best Actor nomination for portraying Freddie Quell in The Master.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He has subsequently earned Best Actor nominations for portraying musician Johnny Cash in the biopic Walk the Line  (  2005  )  and for his role as Freddie Quell , a sex-obsessed alcoholic World War II veteran in the drama film The Master  (  2012  )  , the latter winning him the Volpi Cup for Best Actor .
